Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.23,0:00:04.98,DogDays-narrator,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody on the continent, \Nwe have emergency news!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.65,0:00:09.23,DogDays-narrator,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The tri-country alliance has launched \Nan emergency attack in response
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:12.49,DogDays-narrator,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,to the news that demons have appeared \Nto the south, in the "Dragon's Forest".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.73,0:00:16.96,DogDays-narrator,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, air and land forces from \NBiscotti, Galette, and Pastillage
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.96,0:00:18.64,DogDays-narrator,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,are heading to attack the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.55,0:00:21.48,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,This is not a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:24.50,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,It's a tri-country alliance \Nattack on the demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.50,0:00:28.50,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,The tri-country broadcasting federation \Nwill keep you as up to date as we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.14,0:02:08.98,DogDays-ep-title,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,1)}Decisive Battle! The Dragon's Forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.82,0:02:06.83,DogDays-main-top,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Biscotti forces are in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.83,0:02:08.98,DogDays-main-top,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Pastillage forces are, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.44,0:02:11.31,DogDays-main-top,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Galette forces, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:15.82,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll go over where we are right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.40,0:02:19.41,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,The demon we're attacking
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.69,0:02:21.66,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,is known as the "Dragon Eater".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.93,0:02:25.02,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It invades the land, the \Nplants and the creatures,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.02,0:02:27.09,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,and makes copies of itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.72,0:02:30.29,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's a dangerous parasite-type demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.20,0:02:34.29,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Any animals it eats become part of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.29,0:02:37.48,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,and become branches that send \Nnutrients to the main dragon eater.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.04,0:02:40.40,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,It's bad enough that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.40,0:02:42.50,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,many animals are being attacked, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:47.31,DogDays-main,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,The True Dragons which control \Nthe power of nature live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.57,0:02:50.64,DogDays-main,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,If they're attacked and controlled,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.64,0:02:52.56,DogDays-main,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,it could cause a huge disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.22,0:02:55.57,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Not just for this forest \Nor the surrounding areas,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.06,0:02:58.12,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,but potentially the whole continent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.12,0:03:01.92,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,So we and the Dragon Priestess  \Nwill work together
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.92,0:03:05.24,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,to protect the true dragons
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.24,0:03:06.83,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,and destroy the dangerous demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.47,0:03:10.15,DogDays-main,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.45,0:03:12.22,DogDays-main,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,The rulers of the Three \NCountries and their Heroes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.22,0:03:14.59,DogDays-main,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,all have their treasure swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.15,0:03:16.21,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Once again it's time
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.70,0:03:18.96,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,for the three countries to come together!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:25.22,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Today it's not a war game \Nto entertain everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.50,0:03:27.72,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,It's a war to protect everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.46,0:03:30.31,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.70,0:03:32.33,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.35,0:03:36.44,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,We will protect the True Dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.27,0:03:39.16,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Galette will protect the \NFire Dragon at the Volcano.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.96,0:03:42.53,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Biscotti will protect the \NThunder Dragon at the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.85,0:03:45.45,DogDays-main,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,Pastillage will protect the \NHarvest Dragon in the forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:48.14,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,And the Heroes will use their high speed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:51.05,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,to hunt down the demon along \Nwith the Dragon Priestess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.05,0:03:52.01,DogDays-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.89,0:03:53.95,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Priestess...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.18,0:03:58.00,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive us for allowing humans to run free
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:03:59.46,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,in the Dragon's Forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.48,0:04:03.68,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,It's to keep this forest \Nand the continent safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:05.86,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Please allow it for a short time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.69,0:04:07.39,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:11.46,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.26,0:04:30.55,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:34.96,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.31,0:04:37.89,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! Seven Tale!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:43.09,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Are you two okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.43,0:04:45.39,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.39,0:04:49.10,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,These tentacles are slimy and nasty...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.89,0:04:57.01,DogDays-main,E,0000,0000,0000,,There they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.35,0:04:59.77,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Demons sighted. There's an \Nincredible number of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.45,0:05:01.70,DogDays-main,E,0000,0000,0000,,We'll attack first!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:03.35,DogDays-main,E,0000,0000,0000,,Archers, ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:10.52,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Pastillage Sky Knights Squad Two is \Nbeginning combat with the flyers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.55,0:05:17.21,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Biscotti's main force has \Ndeployed their defenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:22.09,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The Pastillage Air Force is in combat \Nwith approximately 800 demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:26.01,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,An army of demons has appeared \Nin front of the Galette camp!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.31,0:05:27.68,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,1500 more!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.83,0:05:30.37,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,More and more keep appearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.94,0:05:33.22,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,There are about 10,000 in the allied armies,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.45,0:05:35.33,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,so we still have the advantage, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:38.23,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,If the number of demons goes above that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:39.37,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.67,0:05:41.61,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,We'll find the main demon before that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:53.41,DogDays-main,Go,0000,0000,0000,,Maintain defensive formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.13,0:05:56.07,DogDays-main,Go,0000,0000,0000,,Only attack the demons that charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.07,0:05:57.16,DogDays-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:07.17,DogDays-main,Ga,0000,0000,0000,,Hero Crystal... activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.11,0:06:21.06,DogDays-main,Ga,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:22.69,DogDays-main,Ga,0000,0000,0000,,I'll crush you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.57,0:06:38.01,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yukikaze-style Ninjutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.01,0:06:39.33,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Senka Reppuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.32,0:06:43.45,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.45,0:06:44.46,DogDays-main,E,0000,0000,0000,,Yukki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.75,0:06:48.84,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.84,0:06:50.40,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.40,0:06:52.93,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You're taking something \Nto the Heroes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:08.74,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Fire support, second round, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.13,0:07:10.15,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.69,0:07:15.59,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.59,0:07:17.64,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The chief's opened a path!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.78,0:07:22.75,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.14,0:07:25.13,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,The True Dragons are crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:39.11,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,True Dragon-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:44.15,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,The True Dragons are starting \Nto turn into demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:47.40,DogDays-main,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,Stopping that from happening is our job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:49.95,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.71,0:07:53.21,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you turn into Demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:04.48,DogDays-main,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.07,0:08:06.42,DogDays-main,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't blame me for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:15.73,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.47,0:08:19.52,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning Dragon-san, I'll save you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.52,0:08:21.93,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,So hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:26.34,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,You must be suffering,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.89,0:08:28.45,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,but hang in just a little while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:34.44,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Just stay there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:36.82,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Lion King Exploding Thunder Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:45.37,DogDays-internal,L,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, Heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:47.63,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.94,0:08:50.63,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The battle is already getting fierce!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.01,0:08:53.62,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The light you just saw near the volcano
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.62,0:08:55.24,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,was probably Leo's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:01.08,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The flyers have a wide range.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.38,0:09:03.64,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Squad Eight, lead the
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:05.49,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,reporters down to a safe altitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.49,0:09:06.28,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.15,0:09:08.90,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.21,0:09:11.90,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,The humans are standing up to Dragons...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.45,0:09:15.15,DogDays-main,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,Those are our rulers, \Nand we're very proud of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:17.91,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's the ruler's job to protect the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:20.91,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,And it's the Hero's job to save the country
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:24.91,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,when it's in danger and bring \Nsmiles and happiness to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:28.73,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I want everybody to smile, \Nso I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:38.02,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,We found the Dragon Eater.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.36,0:09:40.22,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Hero Rebecca, climb!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.22,0:09:41.10,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.11,0:09:46.60,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,If I can finish him...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.18,0:10:18.68,DogDays-main,Ga,0000,0000,0000,,They just keep coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.06,0:10:21.01,DogDays-main,Ga,0000,0000,0000,,There's no end to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:24.43,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I hope the Heroes can do something soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:25.68,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.46,0:10:38.58,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We need to help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.93,0:10:40.34,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You go in from above, Shinku!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.34,0:10:43.15,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill those roots from below!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.15,0:10:44.24,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:18.37,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,There's no end to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.11,0:11:31.27,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.27,0:11:33.07,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Priestess?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.52,0:11:34.38,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.82,0:11:36.69,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,They won't hit anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.99,0:11:38.56,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,So focus on aiming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.62,0:11:50.02,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,If everybody's in trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:51.52,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.06,0:12:03.39,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,This is Shinku's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:14.45,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hero Crystal...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:15.88,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.23,0:12:28.56,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hero Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.25,0:12:45.16,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Flame King Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.11,0:13:06.18,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Shinku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.43,0:13:08.97,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yukki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:10.34,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Shinku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.34,0:13:13.12,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad you're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.12,0:13:15.69,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yukki... I can't breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.16,0:13:18.56,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:23.97,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Did you bring me that Hero Crystal?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.97,0:13:26.54,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I carried it part of the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.54,0:13:29.07,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,but it just flew off on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.75,0:13:32.98,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,The Hero Crystal must've
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.98,0:13:35.73,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,wanted to see its master.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.03,0:13:36.74,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.78,0:13:39.34,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody's in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:41.12,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,We have to go help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.12,0:13:41.75,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.75,0:13:44.34,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,We'll bring these crystals to
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:46.84,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca and Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.37,0:13:54.98,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:02.73,DogDays-main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Shinku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.97,0:14:04.74,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Becky! \NTake this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:09.74,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,A Demon God Crystal...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.07,0:14:11.66,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I have this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:15.25,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Demon God Crystal, Activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.16,0:14:34.96,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,This is my Hero Crystal?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.96,0:14:38.38,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little different than the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.38,0:14:41.02,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Adel-sama prepared it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.51,0:14:44.27,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,She says its a Spirit Crystal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.27,0:14:47.07,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, here I go then!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.03,0:14:51.53,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit Crystal, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:20.56,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,The transformation's complete?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:23.81,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's the power of water and ice,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.12,0:15:26.55,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,to let you walk with the flames \Nand thunder of Leo-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:27.69,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.63,0:15:30.78,DogDays-narrator,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Fierce battles are still being
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:32.88,DogDays-narrator,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,reported all around the area!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.68,0:15:39.54,DogDays-narrator,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, the demon itself seems \Nto be getting bigger and bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:40.79,DogDays-narrator,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Couver-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:44.26,DogDays-main,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably absorbing the power \Nof the Dragons and the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.03,0:15:47.05,DogDays-main,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, it will absorb
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:49.16,DogDays-main,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,the power of the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.71,0:15:52.06,DogDays-main,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.06,0:15:55.35,DogDays-main,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,Our Heroes will stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.81,0:15:57.00,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.90,0:16:01.10,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,The Heroes will finish this soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.37,0:16:03.35,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Bullet card: full open!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:05.61,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.75,0:16:34.84,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Sharl!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:19.86,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,It's beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.86,0:17:21.52,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,What is this light?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.93,0:17:25.64,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,The power of the land and the dragons \Nthat the Dragon Eater absorbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.90,0:17:29.90,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming down from the sky \Nand going back to the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:32.21,DogDays-main,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,A light of purification and renewal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.21,0:17:34.90,DogDays-main,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,It's the phenomenon known \Nas the Dragon's Tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.10,0:17:37.53,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:40.28,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Joy and blessings come to the land
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.61,0:17:42.53,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,where the Dragon's Tears fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.53,0:17:43.48,DogDays-main,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.98,0:17:45.03,DogDays-main,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.73,0:17:47.73,DogDays-main,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,this rain of light is
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:49.92,DogDays-main,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,a little bit odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.47,0:17:54.09,DogDays-main,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,Any equipment or clothes \Nenchanted with guardian power
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.09,0:17:56.43,DogDays-main,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,that it touches will react, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.80,0:18:05.19,DogDays-main,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,Like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.19,0:18:07.31,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,That's a big problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.41,0:18:12.32,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure chaos is breaking \Nout everywhere, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.99,0:18:17.32,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not going to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:20.82,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it's good for you, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.76,0:18:29.48,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,You heard her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.48,0:18:31.59,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to Flan-san in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.83,0:18:34.09,DogDays-narrator,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm here in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:36.09,DogDays-narrator,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The demon has completely shut down,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:39.77,DogDays-narrator,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,and the black clouds above the \Nforest are gradually clearing up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.38,0:18:43.36,DogDays-narrator,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The war against the demons seems to be
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.36,0:18:45.35,DogDays-narrator,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,ending with a victory for \Nthe tri-country alliance!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.07,0:18:48.35,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I caused you a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.76,0:18:49.98,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:51.67,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Are the dragons okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.67,0:18:53.11,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.43,0:18:57.32,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually they'll wake up and \Neverything will go back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:19:00.74,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,The forest should be even \Nmore bountiful than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.74,0:19:01.62,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.56,0:19:04.12,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Hero Shinku...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.86,0:19:10.12,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.63,0:19:12.95,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:24.61,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.92,0:19:27.74,DogDays-main,I,0000,0000,0000,,Just like I thought, \Nthere was nothing for us to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.32,0:19:32.15,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,It's a sign that the new \Ngeneration is growing up right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.47,0:19:36.47,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,But we need to seal it properly,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.41,0:19:41.16,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,so that it doesn't revive as a sad demon...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:44.53,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually I'll teach \Nthat to Yukikaze and Noir
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:46.41,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.89,0:19:49.70,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to the Dragon Priestess Sharl,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.70,0:19:52.13,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,and the heroes of the tri-country alliance,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.13,0:19:54.17,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,the forest was saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:57.57,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,All knights and soldiers who fought,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.57,0:19:59.22,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.68,0:20:01.36,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,The response team is going to
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.36,0:20:04.48,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,seal the demon we defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.90,0:20:07.07,DogDays-main,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.07,0:20:10.58,DogDays-main,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,Once we get back, we'll have a detailed report
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.58,0:20:12.71,DogDays-main,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,for the citizens and other countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.29,0:20:16.01,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's get ready to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.34,0:20:20.61,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,You're leaving already, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:21.82,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.84,0:20:24.06,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,If you like...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.25,0:20:27.83,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Can we come back to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.35,0:20:31.98,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.51,0:20:34.25,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:39.01,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Once I'm sure the forest has calmed down...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:45.02,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.08,0:20:49.26,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet again,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.76,0:20:51.03,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Hero Shinku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.47,0:21:02.61,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,The summoning accident surprised me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.20,0:21:05.70,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,but I guess it worked out for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.39,0:21:09.12,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,It was a huge mess involving \Nall three countries,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.52,0:21:12.45,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,but you could say we discovered \Nthe problem fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:15.62,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now it's finally back to \Nour peaceful, everyday lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.29,0:21:18.29,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,I've got places for us to \Ngo eat, and things to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.29,0:21:20.26,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a whole plan laid out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.26,0:21:21.06,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.64,0:21:24.38,DogDays-main,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to be busy today,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.89,0:21:26.74,DogDays-main,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,but starting tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.74,0:21:29.25,DogDays-main,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,we can go back to our original \Nplan of relaxing with everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.91,0:21:30.69,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.65,0:21:32.72,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.72,0:21:35.49,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Once again, I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.49,0:21:37.15,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,I was so worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.52,0:21:40.29,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'm truly glad that you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.75,0:21:43.15,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Once we get back, let's relax, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.98,0:21:45.70,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go on a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:47.66,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! Every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.96,0:23:33.61,DogDays-main-top,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all have a baked sweet potato \Nparty to celebrate our victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.97,0:23:35.56,DogDays-main-top,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,We'll cook meat, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.56,0:23:36.38,DogDays-main-top,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,Chomp, chomp!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.38,0:23:37.62,DogDays-main-top,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,It's so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.93,0:23:39.93,DogDays-next-ep-title,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,1)}What's Passed On
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.62,0:23:39.30,DogDays-main-top,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,See you next time!
